### API Testing for Simulation Endpoints
### Base URL (adjust if needed)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api

###
# Test basic API
GET {{baseUrl}}

###
# 1. Start a new simulation
POST {{baseUrl}}/runsimulation?vx=1000&vy=500&vz=0&dx=50000&dy=10000&dz=0&mass=1000000
Content-Type: application/json

###
# 2. Start another simulation with different parameters
POST {{baseUrl}}/runsimulation?vx=2000&vy=1000&vz=500&dx=75000&dy=25000&dz=5000&mass=500000
Content-Type: application/json

###
# 3. Start a third simulation
POST {{baseUrl}}/runsimulation?vx=1500&vy=750&vz=250&dx=100000&dy=50000&dz=10000&mass=750000
Content-Type: application/json

###
# 4. Check simulation results - ID 1
GET {{baseUrl}}/simulationresults?id=1

